{"name":"Ariel Grimwill","size":"small","type":"humanoid","tag":"goblin","alignment":"neutral good","hitDice":"6","armorName":"none","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":7,"otherArmorDesc":"10","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":true,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"48 (6d6)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"10","dexPoints":"17","conPoints":"14","intPoints":"18","wisPoints":"13","chaPoints":"12","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"60","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"6","customCr":"1 (200 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The monster can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The monster regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the monster can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the monster can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The monster can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the monster's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the monster's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the monster dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Fury of the Small","desc":"When [MON] damage a creature with an attack or a spell and the creature's size is larger than yours, she can cause the attack or spell to deal extra damage to the creature. The extra damage is 6. Once she uses this trait, she can't use it again until she finishes a short or long rest."},{"name":"Nimble Escape","desc":"[MON] can take the Disengage or Hide action as a bonus action on each of her turns."},{"name":"Arcane Recovery","desc":"Once per day when [MON] finishes a short rest, she can choose expended spell slots up to 5th level to recover. The spell slots can have a combined level that is equal to or less than 3."},{"name":"Awakened Spellbook","desc":"While [MON] is holding the awakened spellbook, it grants her the following benefits:\n- She can use the book as a spellcasting focus for her wizard spells.\n- When she casts a wizard spell with a spell slot, she can temporarily replace its damage type with a type that appears in another spell in her spellbook, which magically alters the spell's formula for this casting only. The latter spell must be of the same level as the spell slot she expends.\n- When she casts a wizard spell as a ritual, she can use the spell's normal casting time, rather than adding 10 minutes to it. Once she uses this benefit, she can't do so again until she finishes a long rest.\n If necessary, she can replace the book over the course of a short rest by using her Wizardly Quill to write arcane sigils in a blank book or magic spellbok to which she's attuned. At the end of the rest, her spellbook's consciousness is summoned into the new book, along with all its spells. If the previous book still existed somewhere, all the spells vanish from its pages."},{"name":"Spellcasting","desc":"[MON] is a 6th-level spellcaster. Her spellcasting ability is Intelligence (spell save DC [INT SAVE], [INT ATK] to hit with spell attacks). [MON] has the 10 of the following spells prepared:\n\n> Cantrips (at will): _Frostbite, Mage Hand, Mending, Message_\n> 1st level (4 slots): _Alarm, Comprehend Languages, Find Familiar, Identify, Illusory Script, Injurious Spellbook, Mage Armor, Silvery Barbs_\n> 2nd level (3 slots): _Blindness/Deafness, Heartache, Invisibility, Knock_\n> 3rd level (3 slots): _Counterspell, Dispel Magic, Leomund's Tiny Hut, Sending_\n> Ritual Only Spells: _Speak with Animals, Detect Magic_\n\nIf she gains spells, write them on the back of the spellcard."}],"actions":[{"name":"Dagger","desc":"_Melee or Ranged Weapon Attack:_ [DEX ATK] to hit, reach 5 ft. or range 20/60 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [DEX 1D4] piercing damage."},{"name":"Light Crossbow","desc":"_Ranged Weapon Attack:_ [DEX ATK] to hit, range 80/320 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [DEX 1D8] piercing damage."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Wizardly Quill","desc":"[MON] can magically create a Tiny quill in her free hand. The magic quill has the following properties:\n- The quill doesn't require ink. When she writes with it, it produces ink in a color of her choice on the writing surface.\n- The time she must spend to copy a spell into her spellbook equals 2 minutes per spell level if she use the quill for the transcription.\n- [MON] can erase anything she writes with the quill if she waves the feather over the text as a bonus action, provide the text is within 5 feet of her.\n The quill disappears if she creates another one or dies."},{"name":"Manifest Mind (1 / Long Rest)","desc":"While the book is on [MON]'s person, she can cause the mind to manifest as a Tiny spectral object, hovering in an unoccupied space of her choice within 60 feet o her. The spectral mind is intangible and doesn't' occupy its space, and it sheds dim light in a 10-foot radius.\n While manifested, the spectral mind can hear and see, and it has darkvision with a range of 60 feet. The mind can telepathically share with her what it sees and hears (no action required).\n Whenever [MON] casts a wizard spell on her turn, she can cast it as if she was in the spectral mind's space, instead of her own, using its senses. She can do so 3 times per day, and regain all expended uses when she finishes a long rest.\n As a bonus action, she can cause the spectral mind to hover up to 30 feet to an unoccupied space that [MON] or the spectral mind can see. It can pass through creatures but not objects.\n The spectral mind stops manifesting if it is ever more than 300 feet away from [MON], if someone casts dispel magic on it, if the Awakened Spellbook is destroyed, if she dies, or if she dismisses the spectral mind as a bonus action.\n [MON] can expend a spell slot of any level to conjure it again."}],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"int","order":3},{"name":"wis","order":4}],"skills":[{"name":"arcana","stat":"int"},{"name":"history","stat":"int"},{"name":"investigation","stat":"int"},{"name":"religion","stat":"int"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[{"name":"Common","speaks":true},{"name":"Dwarvish","speaks":true},{"name":"Gnomish","speaks":true},{"name":"Goblin","speaks":true}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Ariel","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":4,"damage":[]}